snippet.title: Objector - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In Objector, you play as an enemy of the king. Join the history of opposition against ruthless power in a diverse fantasy world by facing the difficulties and beating bosses waiting for you in challenging gameplay.

Play the demo:
https://objector.itch.io/objector
Visit the Twitter:
https://twitter.com/ObjectorGame
Reddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/ObjectorGame/
Discord:
https://discord.gg/hPc8JFwsZH

Used audio:
